    "title": "Vacancy for Hotel Manager at IndiGo Global Group",
    "description": "Grow your career with IndiGo Global Group! We are hiring a Hotel Manager for our Noida team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout IndiGo Global Group:\nIndiGo Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Learning & development budget\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IndiGo Global Group!",
